## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d60d7-102">可以存储 ASP.NET 页面<xref:System.Web.UI.Page>之间本质上是无状态的 HTTP 请求和响应处理和提供任何网页所需状态。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d60d7-102">ASP.NET pages can store <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> state between the inherently stateless HTTP request and response required to process and serve any Web page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d60d7-103">此状态称为"查看状态"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d60d7-103">This state is called "view state".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d60d7-104">用于存储页面和其控件的视图状态的默认机制是在一个或多个`<hidden>`从 Web 服务器提供给客户端的页面中包含的 HTML 字段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d60d7-104">The default mechanism used to store view state for a page and its controls is in one or more `<hidden>` HTML fields included in the page that is served to a client from a Web server.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d60d7-105"><xref:System.Web.UI.Page>类可以使用<xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister>类来执行此操作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d60d7-105">The <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> class can use the <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> class to do this work.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d60d7-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> 实现<xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Save%2A>和<xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Load%2A>方法<xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister>类，以便<xref:System.Web.UI.Page>可以存储在状态`<hidden>`名为"__VIEWSTATE"Web 客户端上的 HTML 元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d60d7-106"><xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister> implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Save%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.HiddenFieldPageStatePersister.Load%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> class so that the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> can store state in a `<hidden>` HTML element named "__VIEWSTATE" on a Web client.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d60d7-107">当客户端请求同一页上，从 Web 服务器 （回发），`<hidden>`分析元素并将其转换为状态信息的 ASP.NET。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d60d7-107">When the client requests the same page from the Web server (a postback), the `<hidden>` element is parsed and converted to state information by ASP.NET.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d60d7-108">如果<xref:System.Web.UI.Page>请求的实例都有一个相关<xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter>类，它将检索<xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister>从此适配器使用的对象<xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d60d7-108">If the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page> instance that is requested has an associated <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter> class, it retrieves the <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> object from this adapter using the <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d60d7-109">可以重写适配器<xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A>方法以返回<xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister>将页和控件的状态存储在特定的客户端支持某些方法的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d60d7-109">Adapters can override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Adapters.PageAdapter.GetStatePersister%2A> method to return a <xref:System.Web.UI.PageStatePersister> object that stores page and control state in some way that a specific client supports.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d60d7-110">例如，<xref:System.Web.UI.SessionPageStatePersister>类将页和控件的状态存储在 Web 服务器上，而不是客户端，减少了必须发送和存储在客户端可能具有有限的内存和带宽的信息。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d60d7-110">For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.SessionPageStatePersister> class stores page and controls' state on the Web server, instead of the client, to decrease the amount of information that must be sent and stored on a client that has potentially limited memory and bandwidth.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d60d7-111">"_VIEWSTATE"的最大大小`<hidden>`可通过设置 HTML 元素<xref:System.Web.UI.Page.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A>属性或通过<xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A>配置设置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d60d7-111">The maximum size of the "_VIEWSTATE" `<hidden>` HTML element can be set through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Page.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A> property or through the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.PagesSection.MaxPageStateFieldLength%2A> configuration setting.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d60d7-112">当设置此值和"_VIEWSTATE"元素的长度将超过最大长度时，内容被划分多个"_VIEWSTATE"元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d60d7-112">When this value is set and the length of the "_VIEWSTATE" element would exceed the maximum length, the content is divided into multiple "_VIEWSTATE" elements.</span></span>  
  
   
  
